            "issues": "Host \"broken\": (Struct (Encoded side) <-> Struct (Type side))\n\u2514\u2500 Encoded side transformation failure\n   \u2514\u2500 Struct (Encoded side)\n      \u2514\u2500 [\"hostname\"]\n         \u2514\u2500 is missing",
            "mentionsHostname": true
          }
        }
      }
    },
